    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1697850/extras/b670a17cb394f26bdca816c219f1fb96.poster.avif?t=1771891438\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1697850/extras/b670a17cb394f26bdca816c219f1fb96.webm?t=1771891438\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1697850/extras/b670a17cb394f26bdca816c219f1fb96.mp4?t=1771891438\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >赏金任务</h2>投入激烈的战斗，运用灵活性、技巧和智慧，克服可怕的“地下西部”大亨及其仆从。掌握武器技巧，应对各种棘手情况。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1697850/extras/1b5ee318bba3f668b63ff37331a57158.poster.avif?t=1771891438\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1697850/extras/1b5ee318bba3f668b63ff37331a57158.webm?t=1771891438\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1697850/extras/1b5ee318bba3f668b63ff37331a57158.mp4?t=1771891438\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >独特的图像小说风格</h2>精心设计的“地下西部”世界以惊人的手绘动画呈现。跳跃穿越众多面板，灵感源自吉尼·塔塔科夫斯基（《武士杰克》、《原始时代》）的作品。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1697850/extras/4b4d677a549dcb4c2fcb9c7a2dd665af.poster.avif?t=1771891438\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1697850/extras/4b4d677a549dcb4c2fcb9c7a2dd665af.webm?t=1771891438\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1697850/extras/4b4d677a549dcb4c2fcb9c7a2dd665af.mp4?t=1771891438\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >探索荒野西部的地下世界</h2>探索各种充满神秘与绝望的灵魂境界。揭示“地下西部”的诸多秘密，寻找隐藏的真相。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1697850/extras/5bd275d3faf91ac8d95cbe7a417ec8bb.poster.avif?t=1771891438\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1697850/extras/5bd275d3faf91ac8d95cbe7a417ec8bb.webm?t=1771891438\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1697850/extras/5bd275d3faf91ac8d95cbe7a417ec8bb.mp4?t=1771891438\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >伟大的失落与奉献故事</h2>亲历玫瑰的故事，她深陷邪恶的“地下世界之灵”的勒索。跟随她的奥德赛，穿越危险的“地下西部”，解救被困于银锁中的女儿之灵魂。",
